Dialogue: 2,0:11:17.59,0:11:21.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We wanted to see if you'd say "you're gonna burp?"
Dialogue: 2,0:11:22.49,0:11:24.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oh, eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:24.66,0:11:27.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I didn't say it on purpose, it was a reflex
Dialogue: 2,0:11:27.60,0:11:30.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If this was real it'd be bad
Dialogue: 2,0:11:30.47,0:11:33.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I really said it by accident
Dialogue: 2,0:11:33.80,0:11:37.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, the next target is
Dialogue: 2,0:11:37.44,0:11:40.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Toshikazu Miura
Dialogue: 2,0:11:40.83,0:11:46.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is the situation this time that will encourage him to say "you're gonna do it?"
Dialogue: 2,0:11:47.49,0:11:50.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A flash mob marriage proposal
Dialogue: 2,0:11:51.62,0:12:00.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time there will be a flash mob of women sitting on chairs in this open square
Dialogue: 2,0:12:00.88,0:12:03.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The propsal will be made by
Dialogue: 2,0:12:03.94,0:12:08.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A seemingly unconnected person
Dialogue: 2,0:12:23.62,0:12:25.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, the "surprise proposal" has begun
Dialogue: 2,0:12:25.86,0:12:27.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm Toshio
Dialogue: 2,0:12:27.90,0:12:32.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As you can see, the fake show is shot from the beginning
Dialogue: 2,0:12:33.27,0:12:35.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then, on site
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.87,0:12:41.79,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Music seems very appropriate
Dialogue: 2,0:12:46.46,0:12:49.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Without further ado, the flash mob starts
Dialogue: 2,0:12:52.82,0:12:54.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, here we go
Dialogue: 2,0:12:56.40,0:12:58.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not bad. Which one is the boyfriend? Not here yet?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:59.79,0:13:05.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At this point, Toshio is watching in the car
Dialogue: 2,0:13:05.96,0:13:09.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And the scene suddenly shifts at the end
Dialogue: 2,0:13:09.70,0:13:14.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He will witness the moment first hand
Dialogue: 2,0:13:15.89,0:13:19.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You still don't understand the situation, do you?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:19.84,0:13:20.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hasn't figured it out yet
Dialogue: 2,0:13:20.88,0:13:22.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thinking "what's this? It's great"
Dialogue: 2,0:13:30.59,0:13:32.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oh, the number of people has increased
Dialogue: 2,0:13:36.89,0:13:40.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Where's the boyfriend? Hasn't made an appearance yet?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:40.00,0:13:42.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Such a long lead up
Dialogue: 2,0:13:43.13,0:13:45.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then at this point
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.05,0:13:53.42,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Boyfriend-type
Dialogue: 2,0:13:55.13,0:13:59.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Finally someone with the aura of an important person comes into view
Dialogue: 2,0:14:00.41,0:14:01.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 2,0:14:02.91,0:14:06.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah this one? Boyfriend? This is the guy, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:07.30,0:14:10.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Toshio is led correctly
Dialogue: 2,0:14:10.16,0:14:13.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, the verification is setup perfectly
Dialogue: 2,0:14:14.74,0:14:19.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At the moment when the flash mob was approaching its climax
Dialogue: 2,0:14:20.47,0:14:22.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The scene comes to its conclusion
Dialogue: 2,0:14:23.81,0:14:25.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why do I feel so nervous?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:28.75,0:14:30.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.06,0:14:31.55,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So embarrassing
Dialogue: 2,0:14:32.42,0:14:33.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.38,0:14:38.56,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Must think it is the right person
Dialogue: 2,0:14:44.15,0:14:45.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The result?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:59.98,0:15:01.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:05.55,0:15:06.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:07.45,0:15:08.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:08.22,0:15:09.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:11.27,0:15:13.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Couldn't say it
Dialogue: 2,0:15:17.56,0:15:19.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:19.00,0:15:22.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I will make you happy all your life
Dialogue: 2,0:15:22.73,0:15:23.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is it this one?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:23.97,0:15:26.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please marry me
Dialogue: 2,0:15:27.77,0:15:28.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ok
Dialogue: 2,0:15:28.11,0:15:30.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh? Is it supposed to be this guy?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:32.34,0:15:33.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hang on
Dialogue: 2,0:15:33.61,0:15:34.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hey hey hey
Dialogue: 2,0:15:34.35,0:15:35.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:35.81,0:15:37.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm so confused
Dialogue: 2,0:15:37.21,0:15:38.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh? Is he your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:38.48,0:15:41.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, he is. \N -He's your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:42.42,0:15:43.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's you?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:45.26,0:15:46.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:46.72,0:15:48.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not you? No, no, wait
Dialogue: 2,0:15:48.79,0:15:50.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:52.10,0:15:54.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.02,0:15:55.30,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Questioning him non-stop
Dialogue: 2,0:15:57.54,0:15:58.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hooo—
Dialogue: 2,0:15:58.17,0:15:59.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, it's not the time to make a scene
Dialogue: 2,0:15:59.84,0:16:00.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's not the time to make a scene
Dialogue: 2,0:16:01.34,0:16:02.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, no... this...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:02.11,0:16:05.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Congratulations to both of you!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:05.54,0:16:07.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I thought he was the boyfriend
Dialogue: 2,0:16:07.14,0:16:09.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was watching him the whole time
Dialogue: 2,0:16:09.88,0:16:10.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It turned out to be you, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:12.47,0:16:16.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although he made some comments
Dialogue: 2,0:16:16.35,0:16:20.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He didn't say "you're gonna do it?"
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.28,0:16:20.82,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Difficult
Dialogue: 2,0:16:21.35,0:16:23.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, we reveal the truth
Dialogue: 2,0:16:23.23,0:16:24.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work
Dialogue: 2,0:16:24.16,0:16:25.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work
Dialogue: 2,0:16:25.78,0:16:27.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So close. What happened?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:27.77,0:16:30.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is Wednesday Downtown
Dialogue: 2,0:16:30.67,0:16:32.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh, really?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:32.44,0:16:36.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wednesday Downtown?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:36.14,0:16:37.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Just this?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:37.07,0:16:38.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is this... what is it?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:38.78,0:16:40.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is it a test of some theory?\N  -Yes
Dialogue: 2,0:16:40.31,0:16:43.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you're a tsukkomi, you'll say "you're gonna do it?"
Dialogue: 2,0:16:43.25,0:16:45.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, a test of whether you'll do it or not
Dialogue: 2,0:16:45.95,0:16:48.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Whether you'll do it straight away
Dialogue: 2,0:16:48.95,0:16:51.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, no, this is too...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:51.52,0:16:53.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The word "you!?" was stuck in my throat
Dialogue: 2,0:16:53.79,0:16:56.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But I wasn't sure whether it was ok or not...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:56.79,0:16:58.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh~
Dialogue: 2,0:16:59.03,0:17:01.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I want to do it again...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:01.27,0:17:03.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I really wanna hit them with it without thinking
Dialogue: 2,0:17:03.15,0:17:06.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"You're gonna do it?" like that
Dialogue: 2,0:17:06.77,0:17:12.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The last target is
Dialogue: 2,0:17:12.37,0:17:14.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Viking's Kotouge
Dialogue: 2,0:17:14.85,0:17:16.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The key word is
Dialogue: 2,0:17:16.90,0:17:21.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You're gonna jump?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:21.09,0:17:28.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When bungee jumping, after the countdown
Dialogue: 2,0:17:28.17,0:17:31.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The staff will jump instead
Dialogue: 2,0:17:32.23,0:17:33.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You'd think it was an accident
Dialogue: 2,0:17:33.95,0:17:36.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really would
Dialogue: 2,0:17:36.47,0:17:37.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hello, I'm Viking's Kotouge
Dialogue: 2,0:17:38.14,0:17:40.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful day!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:40.07,0:17:42.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Recording on a sunny day
Dialogue: 2,0:17:42.54,0:17:45.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As you can see, a fake program was used to take Kotouge to Gunma Prefecture
Dialogue: 2,0:17:45.96,0:17:51.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,To ensure he doesn't realize, we shoot him wandering outside for 1 hour
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.31,0:17:51.80,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's doing it very seriously
Dialogue: 2,0:17:51.32,0:17:52.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Tasty
Dialogue: 2,0:17:52.12,0:17:55.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next is the famous thing in Minakami-cho, the bungee jump
Dialogue: 2,0:17:55.52,0:17:56.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh~
Dialogue: 2,0:17:56.92,0:17:57.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No no...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:57.92,0:18:00.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't want to! It's awful!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:00.79,0:18:02.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When you are young, you are not afraid of this sort of thing
Dialogue: 2,0:18:02.89,0:18:06.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As I get older, I get more and more afraid
Dialogue: 2,0:18:06.97,0:18:08.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Starting to get scared now
Dialogue: 2,0:18:08.13,0:18:10.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Since I became an old man i've become afraid
Dialogue: 2,0:18:10.90,0:18:13.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A very noticeable emotional plunge
Dialogue: 2,0:18:14.30,0:18:17.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We won't actually make Kotouge jump
Dialogue: 2,0:18:18.43,0:18:22.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But we still lead him to the 42m high bungee jumping platform
Dialogue: 2,0:18:22.68,0:18:25.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Whoooo
Dialogue: 2,0:18:25.02,0:18:27.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can't do this, I can't jump!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:27.59,0:18:29.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So scary, I can't do this
Dialogue: 2,0:18:29.62,0:18:31.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's a no go
Dialogue: 2,0:18:31.95,0:18:33.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Bungee is a no go
Dialogue: 2,0:18:33.82,0:18:36.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I really can't do this
Dialogue: 2,0:18:36.33,0:18:37.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is really impossible
Dialogue: 2,0:18:37.59,0:18:40.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As Kotouge is gripped by fear
Dialogue: 2,0:18:41.93,0:18:46.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The final useless preparations are made
Dialogue: 2,0:18:46.64,0:18:48.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can you stand up?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:48.04,0:18:50.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oh wow this is really impossible
Dialogue: 2,0:18:51.92,0:18:54.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah so scary, oh, wow
Dialogue: 2,0:18:55.05,0:18:55.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So scary!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:56.60,0:18:59.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Finally, it's time to bungee jump
Dialogue: 2,0:18:59.92,0:19:01.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That... although I can
Dialogue: 2,0:19:02.02,0:19:04.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But this is the last time
Dialogue: 2,0:19:04.09,0:19:05.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Last bungee
Dialogue: 2,0:19:05.73,0:19:10.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Will Kotogue say "you're gonna jump?"
Dialogue: 2,0:19:10.90,0:19:12.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, let's get started
Dialogue: 2,0:19:12.60,0:19:14.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Countdown
Dialogue: 2,0:19:14.10,0:19:21.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,10 9 8 7 6 5 4 3
Dialogue: 2,0:19:21.52,0:19:27.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.58,0:19:29.84,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,You'd react like that
Dialogue: 2,0:19:33.17,0:19:36.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Simply not the time to comment
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.62,0:19:45.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,His reaction is the same as if he jumped down himself
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.24,0:19:53.35,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is more like an accident
Dialogue: 2,0:20:00.34,0:20:02.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Jumped yourself
Dialogue: 2,0:20:02.78,0:20:04.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Jumped yourself
Dialogue: 2,0:20:05.47,0:20:08.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eventually, he commented
Dialogue: 2,0:20:08.75,0:20:12.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,However, it's not "you're gonna jump?"
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.92,0:20:12.70,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Its too abnormal
Dialogue: 2,0:20:12.09,0:20:13.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Jumped yourself
Dialogue: 2,0:20:14.50,0:20:17.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, we revealed the truth
Dialogue: 2,0:20:17.80,0:20:19.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work
Dialogue: 2,0:20:22.00,0:20:23.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work
Dialogue: 2,0:20:24.80,0:20:26.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wed?
Dialogue: 2,0:20:26.87,0:20:27.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wed?\N  -Correct
Dialogue: 2,0:20:27.94,0:20:29.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wed?
Dialogue: 2,0:20:29.34,0:20:31.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It was Wed all along...
Dialogue: 2,0:20:31.71,0:20:36.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you're a tsukkomi, you'd immediately say "you're gonna jump?"
Dialogue: 2,0:20:36.41,0:20:38.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No way no way
Dialogue: 2,0:20:38.25,0:20:40.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Absolutely no way
Dialogue: 2,0:20:40.78,0:20:42.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No way
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.16,0:20:42.85,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Looks so happy
Dialogue: 2,0:20:42.29,0:20:44.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no
Dialogue: 2,0:20:44.36,0:20:46.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No way I can say "you're gonna jump?"
Dialogue: 2,0:20:46.89,0:20:49.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The fear is way too dominant
Dialogue: 2,0:20:49.33,0:20:53.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If I was in a more normal mental state
Dialogue: 2,0:20:53.60,0:20:54.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Maybe i'd say it
Dialogue: 2,0:20:54.70,0:20:58.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,On this occasion i'm just engulfed by fear
Dialogue: 2,0:20:58.27,0:20:59.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's impossible to say it
Dialogue: 2,0:21:00.94,0:21:02.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Now I know I don't have to jump
Dialogue: 2,0:21:02.47,0:21:04.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm super happy!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:04.78,0:21:06.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,My voice has gotten louder too
Dialogue: 2,0:21:07.36,0:21:12.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0201FB&\3c&HFFFFFF&}In summary \N{\c\3c}It's hard to say
Dialogue: 2,0:21:13.63,0:21:19.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately only one person did it
Dialogue: 2,0:21:19.94,0:21:22.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you think, would you be able to say it?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:22.47,0:21:26.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At the bungee place, no way
Dialogue: 2,0:21:26.26,0:21:29.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You'd think someone has just died
Dialogue: 2,0:21:30.43,0:21:35.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Only extreme people like Jinnai and Fujimoto would say it
Dialogue: 2,0:21:35.31,0:21:39.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Normal people wont, just these two abnormal ones
Dialogue: 2,0:21:41.35,0:21:47.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But out of all of them Jinnai's worse the most boring
Dialogue: 2,0:21:47.76,0:21:50.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That... please do not say that directly
Dialogue: 2,0:21:50.72,0:21:52.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who could say such a thing?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:53.60,0:21:56.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If it was me i'd surely say it
Dialogue: 2,0:21:56.58,0:21:59.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Looking at each of those I kept thinking i'd say it
Dialogue: 2,0:21:59.43,0:22:01.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I keep thinking, "I'd say it if I were you!"
Dialogue: 2,0:22:01.07,0:22:02.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That is, all five? All of them?
Dialogue: 2,0:22:02.60,0:22:05.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was thinking "Again I would've said it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.11,0:22:07.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I want to see it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.90,0:22:11.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let's welcome the next presenter
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.77,0:22:18.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Knights
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.08,0:22:23.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.22,0:22:23.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.82,0:22:26.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A towel was thrown at me by Kobori
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.91,0:22:30.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.21,0:22:33.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We haven't even gotten over that yet
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:34.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So impactful
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.90,0:22:36.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But also thanks to the program team
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.44,0:22:39.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The number of customers at the Toyokan has increased. \N -Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.26,0:22:41.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, more young people are going
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.09,0:22:43.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's great.  \N-Great
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.86,0:22:45.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's improved the scene
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.12,0:22:50.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A little bit of self-hatred can make the audience laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.14,0:22:53.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Awesome.\N  -But their relationship hasn't changed for the better?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.24,0:22:55.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The relationship is still bad, but there are laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.79,0:22:57.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kyomaru and Kyouhei, who are very close to each other, aren't getting any laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.53,0:23:02.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't make jokes like that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.11,0:23:06.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We thank them for their appearance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.05,0:23:09.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time we bring a theory about "lecturing"\N  -I'm scared
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:14.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Have teachers and seniors at school ever said this to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.17,0:23:17.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"If you don't want to work then get out"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.08,0:23:21.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In fact, even if someone tells you to get lost
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.33,0:23:22.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There's no way you'll actually walk away, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.97,0:23:24.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's true that you wouldn't leave
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.25,0:23:26.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Get out" actually means "don't go"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.42,0:23:28.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's true
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.82,0:23:31.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So this time we bring the following theory
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.28,0:23:36.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Will anyone ever follow the "get out" statement included in a lecture?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.45,0:23:41.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Got it\N  -That's what you'd think, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.49,0:23:44.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Get lost", "get out of here" etc
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.38,0:23:46.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And "Do you know why I am angry?"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.37,0:23:47.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Obon loves to say that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.26,0:23:52.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When it comes to screwing people over\N  -You're really almost done
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.35,0:23:55.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No mention of a disbandment at all, but just angry
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.07,0:23:58.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is it going to be replayed again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.10,0:23:59.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We are not here to replay it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.93,0:24:01.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We've brought a new theory
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.02,0:24:08.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Will anyone ever follow the "get out" statement included in a lecture?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.65,0:24:16.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time, we asked four artists who are kind and not angry types
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.40,0:24:19.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Competition who can use the shortest time to force back the whole target
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.34,0:24:23.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Lecture Elimination Contest
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.04,0:24:27.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The first challenger is
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.09,0:24:30.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nana Suzuki
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.85,0:24:32.43,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,She's not the angry type
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.28,0:24:34.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Good morning\N  -Good morning
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.59,0:24:36.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Good morning
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.14,0:24:39.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The junior about to be lectured is
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.85,0:24:41.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What to drink, what to drink
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.52,0:24:46.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nishino Miki
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.43,0:24:50.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I have a simple question
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.07,0:24:52.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Very puzzled \N-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.20,0:24:59.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After doing a number one in the toilet, do you wipe from the front or back
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.42,0:24:59.96,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is she talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.75,0:25:02.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,From the back. \N -Yes, from the back
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.85,0:25:04.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I am also from the back
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.01,0:25:05.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Will anyone do it from the front?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.75,0:25:08.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I've called about 10 people and asked them
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.45,0:25:14.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nine people from the back, one from the front
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.83,0:25:18.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's hard to imagine that this is a lunchtime girls' gossip
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.54,0:25:20.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In the midst of a heated conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.88,0:25:27.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's finally time for Nana Suzuki, who has never been angry with her juniors, to lecture
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.23,0:25:31.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But I think you are quite powerful, you're often on TV
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.38,0:25:32.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Working hard
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.61,0:25:35.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But actually not
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.71,0:25:39.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I also often search myself online\N  -Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.18,0:25:41.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I search a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.92,0:25:46.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The search results for Nishino Miki are all "super similar to Suzuki Nana"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.29,0:25:50.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Super similar" or something like that
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.09,0:25:50.43,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's starting to get a little scary
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.43,0:25:54.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This really makes me stressed out
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.30,0:25:58.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, stress?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.94,0:26:02.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Body movements too
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.37,0:26:06.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I hope you won't talk like that again
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.68,0:26:09.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No way... you mean me?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.80,0:26:15.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She asks the other to change her persona
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.23,0:26:18.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This far-fetched excuse is used to start the lecture
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.82,0:26:22.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I often gesture a lot when I speak
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.63,0:26:28.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's what i'm known for
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.46,0:26:33.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So I hope that when you are on TV in the future
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.90,0:26:35.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't make hand gestures
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.06,0:26:36.37,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So scary
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.37,0:26:38.81,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's scary to be told that
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.81,0:26:40.26,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's painful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.26,0:26:42.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.54,0:26:47.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nishino is hesitant to let her claim this privilege which is not a privilege
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.52,0:26:53.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next time you're on TV, don't make hand gestures
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.46,0:26:56.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And don't let people say you look like Suzuki Nana. Can you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.08,0:27:00.97,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is there an answer for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.82,0:27:00.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.09,0:27:04.42,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It is very difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.23,0:27:06.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But... I don't do it purposely
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.14,0:27:08.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you don't understand what I mean you can leave now
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.87,0:27:15.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That... I can't leave
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.12,0:27:15.81,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Scary enough
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.81,0:27:19.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But you don't understand me at all! \N -No, I understand everything
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.49,0:27:21.55,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sitting still is also a bit difficult to do
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.11,0:27:25.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At this point, the first "get out" is sent out a little early
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.78,0:27:27.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is she proficient
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.19,0:27:29.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seems like she's used to it
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.37,0:27:34.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But the junior Nishino will not go so easily
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.77,0:27:37.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you don't understand, get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.00,0:27:38.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Get out now
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.94,0:27:41.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How can I change it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.77,0:27:42.44,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Feels like she has a lot of anger
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.31,0:27:43.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I will try...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.57,0:27:45.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Just wear handcuffs on TV, isn't that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.28,0:27:47.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wearing handcuffs on TV...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.68,0:27:49.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That way you can't make gestures
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.51,0:27:51.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hand gestures are not possible
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.05,0:27:51.33,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.28,0:27:53.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But then I won't get screentime
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.95,0:27:55.10,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's true that it can't be broadcast
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.29,0:27:56.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I really did not mean to imitate you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.46,0:27:58.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Just unconsciously
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.89,0:28:00.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No hand gestures now either
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.62,0:28:03.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFEC3E&\1a&H75&\3c&H000000&\3a&HA1&}Ah, sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.13,0:28:04.16,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,No hand gestures allowed
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.16,0:28:05.00,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.70,0:28:06.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Now go or get handcuffed
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.83,0:28:08.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Go or get handcuffed?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.41,0:28:14.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At this point, the ultimate choice of "leaving" or "handcuffs" is presented
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.09,0:28:17.07,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not moving at all
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.97,0:28:20.85,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Staring blankly!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.85,0:28:22.37,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What to do? \N -No, no, no
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.99,0:28:24.44,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Go or handcuffs
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.65,0:28:27.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next, a silent showdown
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.44,0:28:28.69,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,She lasted so long
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.69,0:28:30.62,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's been five minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.62,0:28:32.85,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Super scary
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.29,0:28:36.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll go
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.26,0:28:39.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seriously, go
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.03,0:28:42.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really, go now  {\c&HFFEC3E&\1a&H8D&\3c&H000000&\3a&H88&}\N-Ok
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.91,0:28:44.21,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.21,0:28:45.64,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.64,0:28:46.92,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's scary, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.54,0:28:50.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Get out of here!  {\c&HFFEC3E&\1a&H80&\3c&H000000&\3a&HA8&}\N-That...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.04,0:28:53.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.26,0:28:53.84,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.34,0:28:55.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Scary as hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.17,0:28:57.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Way too scary
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.33,0:29:00.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's really too scary, Nana-chan...  \N-It's awful
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.88,0:29:03.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Get the hell out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.25,0:29:07.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.68,0:29:12.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, Suzuki Nana ended at 6 minutes and 24 seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.33,0:29:14.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Here we revealed the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.96,0:29:16.90,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Poor thing
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.37,0:29:19.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.20,0:29:19.17,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why's she escaping?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.32,0:29:21.81,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,We're on the same side
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.12,0:29:26.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nishino, who hadn't fully understood the situation, returned to Suzuki's side
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.72,0:29:29.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.41,0:29:32.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really scared me. \N -Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.48,0:29:35.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I thought i'd been cursed
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.03,0:29:38.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Possessed by an evil spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.32,0:29:40.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's fake, not real
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.99,0:29:44.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I thought that if I left, we would never see each other again
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.66,0:29:46.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Goodbye forever
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.50,0:29:47.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So happy. Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.17,0:29:50.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.98,0:29:52.06,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Still afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.43,0:29:52.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm really scared to death
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.08,0:29:55.13,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Real feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.38,0:29:56.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The next target is
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.95,0:30:00.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Viking's Nishimura
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.44,0:30:03.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Confident?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.04,0:30:04.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How can I say it? I am a person who
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.97,0:30:10.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,First of all, I don't lecture juniors
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.69,0:30:14.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Never get angry either
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.09,0:30:17.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,By the way, have you ever been told to "get out"?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.83,0:30:19.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I have before
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.56,0:30:21.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.36,0:30:23.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A manager gave me his card
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.97,0:30:28.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When I was given it I said "ok, i'll pay with this"
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.04,0:30:31.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then I put four or five rounds on the card
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.58,0:30:35.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The next day, after he found out, I was told to get out
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.28,0:30:38.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did you really leave?\N  -I left
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.72,0:30:42.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The kind of man who will walk away on demand
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.73,0:30:47.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can he get others to flee or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.79,0:30:51.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A public performance
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.29,0:30:54.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,can get 50,000 or 60,000 at that time. \N -Great
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.80,0:30:56.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But that's about it. It's only on occasion
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.60,0:31:00.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Before King of Conte I got 40,000 at most
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.40,0:31:04.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, i've taken over then
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.96,0:31:07.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They tentatively have a casual conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.81,0:31:13.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,One pork hot pot, please
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.28,0:31:14.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is it for two people?\N -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.99,0:31:18.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ok then
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.79,0:31:23.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After the clerk leaves, the lecture begins
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.33,0:31:27.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What did you order?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.13,0:31:29.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ordered hot pot
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.73,0:31:31.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hot pot?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.90,0:31:34.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hot pot?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.10,0:31:35.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hot pot?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.54,0:31:37.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.82,0:31:35.73,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is this ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.73,0:31:38.26,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,No way, why would you be angry about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.91,0:31:40.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hot pot?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.21,0:31:42.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.43,0:31:42.34,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Clearly heard it at the time
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.78,0:31:44.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How many servings?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.88,0:31:46.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For two
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.12,0:31:48.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Are you looking down on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.14,0:31:48.21,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.12,0:31:52.83,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Too weird
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.69,0:31:54.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,With the Hot pot order as the first issue
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.22,0:31:57.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nishimura devises a fascinating setting
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.86,0:32:01.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A taste minefield
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.77,0:32:04.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You can't get it right!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.67,0:32:05.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.10,0:32:07.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You should understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.97,0:32:11.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You just don't get it \N -I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.21,0:32:11.28,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It sucks
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.01,0:32:13.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Enough, you can go for today
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.91,0:32:15.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.92,0:32:19.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Here the "get out" is launched
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.95,0:32:21.41,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's impossible, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.42,0:32:23.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.62,0:32:26.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,All right, just get out
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.56,0:32:30.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did you order hot pot?  \N-Yes, I did
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.29,0:32:34.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then get out of here.\N  -I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.66,0:32:37.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's too uninspiring
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.03,0:32:38.52,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,You have to eat alone if he leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.23,0:32:38.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.40,0:32:41.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think this is more balanced
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.07,0:32:45.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What the hell is hot pot, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.24,0:32:46.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sukiyaki is more like it
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.18,0:32:49.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why order hot pot?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.61,0:32:53.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's impossible to order hot pot normally
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.58,0:32:55.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hot pot...sorry\N  -Get out
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.89,0:33:00.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I was wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.66,0:33:02.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please don't make me go
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.83,0:33:06.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, you're really off the mark
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.36,0:33:07.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's obviously you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.00,0:33:10.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is the Achilles heel of comedians
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.40,0:33:12.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What kind of hot pot did you order?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.67,0:33:14.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It should be Sukiyaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.34,0:33:18.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The correct answer is neither hot pot nor sukiyaki
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.29,0:33:22.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But the off-the-mark Nishimura is at least interesting as a comedian
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.46,0:33:24.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Even so
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.68,0:33:28.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What are the vegetables in sukiyaki and hot pot?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.42,0:33:30.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,First, Sukiyaki
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.62,0:33:33.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Chrysanthemum  \N-Mmmm
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.59,0:33:35.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Cabbage\N  -Mmm
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.73,0:33:38.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Carrot \N -Mmm
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.40,0:33:41.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Konjaku \N -Konjaku is not a vegetable
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.77,0:33:44.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You should really get out of here
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.07,0:33:48.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why can't you read out the vegetables in sukiyaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.51,0:33:49.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are many more
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.77,0:33:50.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Onion
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.57,0:33:53.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. Onions are perfect.\N  -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.28,0:33:56.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You should really get out of here. \N -Sorry, sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.25,0:33:57.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sincerely get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.51,0:34:01.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You can't even tell me the ingredients of sukiyaki, you're not even close to being good enough.\N  -I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.95,0:34:05.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sukiyaki has much higher status than shabu-shabu\N  -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.92,0:34:07.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'll remember
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.46,0:34:09.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.76,0:34:13.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seriously, really need to get out of here. \N-Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.00,0:34:15.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you don't understand this... \N -I'll go
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.67,0:34:20.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What can I do? \N -Sorry, this guy won't leave
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.57,0:34:24.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please get him out of here\N -Shall I make him go away?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.17,0:34:25.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please get him out of here
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.21,0:34:29.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'll leave now
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.58,0:34:31.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Miss, I'm sorry. It's okay
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.82,0:34:36.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Miss, please take him out
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.52,0:34:37.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Get him out of here
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.72,0:34:40.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'll go by myself. It's fine
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.29,0:34:42.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You should really get out of here.\N  -I'm sorry. I get it
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.56,0:34:44.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Get the hell out of here! \N  -I'm so sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.38,0:34:49.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Using the rough trick of getting the staff's help
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.25,0:34:52.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nishimura achieves success after 12 minutes 38 seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.64,0:34:53.81,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't cause others trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.38,0:34:56.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The next challenger is
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.66,0:35:00.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Panther's Ogata
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.52,0:35:03.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The target is
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.70,0:35:05.77,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's Takashi
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.71,0:35:06.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Just the two of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.74,0:35:11.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Trendy Angel's Takashi
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.50,0:35:15.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As the presenter you should have done it yourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.70,0:35:17.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But after watching the VTR just now
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.95,0:35:21.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For authenticity, Obon Kobon would be better
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.32,0:35:22.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.34,0:35:24.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Get out of here! \N It's happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.77,0:35:29.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next is Panther's Ogata
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.64,0:35:30.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.74,0:35:35.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I've never met an Ogata fan
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.78,0:35:38.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's not right, there are some
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.85,0:35:41.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ogata fans don't exist, right? \N-They do
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.09,0:35:45.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He mistakenly chose a junior who is used to messing around
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.46,0:35:48.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Making it difficult to start the lecture
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.68,0:35:56.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,However, after an hour, finally
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.54,0:36:05.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,My child. You held her when you came to my house
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.11,0:36:10.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Didn't you feel her up?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.06,0:36:11.16,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.45,0:36:15.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When holding her
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.83,0:36:16.80,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's disgusting
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.69,0:36:17.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I just held her normally
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.76,0:36:20.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.53,0:36:22.11,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,A bad vibe
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.79,0:36:24.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Due to struggling to find a point to lecture on
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.27,0:36:28.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ogata becomes angry for no reason
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.41,0:36:30.18,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Impressive
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.83,0:36:33.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Your persona is that type
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.17,0:36:38.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I hope you can pay attention to how you make contact
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.10,0:36:41.39,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not listening at all
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.44,0:36:44.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But everyone would do it in this way \N-They wouldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.45,0:36:47.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, get out
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.49,0:36:51.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'll leave later
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.22,0:36:53.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's not a matter of a when
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.62,0:36:56.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I told you to go now.\N  -In a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.56,0:37:00.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What? Are you t underestimating me? Sitting their vaping
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.30,0:37:02.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I am now really angry
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.80,0:37:04.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.43,0:37:06.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Saying sorry but still smoking?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.84,0:37:11.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No smoking
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.74,0:37:14.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You get out of here, I'm really in a bad mood
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.22,0:37:16.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But after that
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.78,0:37:21.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No drinking
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.15,0:37:25.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You are completely ignoring me
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.86,0:37:29.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I am 41 years old, how old are you?\NHow old are you?  -33
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.26,0:37:31.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,33 years old
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.16,0:37:32.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You're not taking me seriously
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.33,0:37:35.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No drinking
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.23,0:37:39.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm 8 years older than you
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.00,0:37:43.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But I was born earlier in the month \N -That has nothing to do with anything, okay!?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.59,0:37:48.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The idiotic conversation went on like this for more than 15 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.18,0:37:52.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And Takashi eventually stands up out of boredom
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.35,0:37:54.10,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Bored
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.62,0:37:54.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.85,0:37:57.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry for what? I can't forgive you
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.45,0:37:59.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Get out of here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.14,0:38:02.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The final challenger is
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.11,0:38:05.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,DJ KOO
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.10,0:38:09.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Today you'll be lecturing
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.50,0:38:13.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do you usually get angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.51,0:38:19.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm not very loud...loud... lou-
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.88,0:38:25.28,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do it properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.64,0:38:21.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You already know the content, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.58,0:38:24.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Curry? The case of the curry department?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.30,0:38:32.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The lecture is given at the Avex-Management Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.45,0:38:36.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,To Hama, a junior who starred with KOO
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.13,0:38:41.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Many new projects will be held in 2019
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.03,0:38:42.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Special events
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.83,0:38:50.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Have you written down a few of your ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.44,0:38:51.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is it written on paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.73,0:38:53.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Idea list
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.31,0:38:56.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I didn't write it down \N -Why? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.51,0:38:59.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait, wait a little bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.38,0:39:01.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait a second
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.02,0:39:07.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You... \N-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.36,0:39:10.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to do it, don't do it
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.69,0:39:11.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't do it
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.53,0:39:12.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You can leave today
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.16,0:39:15.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry, you can go now
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.70,0:39:19.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A sudden increase in horsepower smoothly leads to the request
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.76,0:39:21.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A perfect transition
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.17,0:39:22.76,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Suddenly so scary
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.85,0:39:23.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,However
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.87,0:39:27.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For example, what do you think about the curry scene in the future
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.98,0:39:29.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.25,0:39:34.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The scene of curry. Tell me about it from your point of view
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.45,0:39:36.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Curry scene?\N  -The curry scene
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.19,0:39:39.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Similar to the "music scene" and "hip-hop scene"
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.92,0:39:43.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's already very popular
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.29,0:39:49.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The curry department should make the atmosphere hotter\N -Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.75,0:39:49.84,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.39,0:39:55.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Where did the momentum go?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.60,0:39:59.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The unaccustomed lecturing suddenly cools down
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.04,0:40:03.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I often go to Shimokitazawa Curry Music Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.01,0:40:06.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Shimokitazawa Curry Music Festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.42,0:40:09.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Very popular now
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.74,0:40:09.72,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Taking notes
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.49,0:40:11.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,More stores than in Jimbocho
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.22,0:40:12.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are more than one hundred
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.49,0:40:16.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is what I want you to write about
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.78,0:40:21.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's too focused on this meeting of the curry department
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.12,0:40:20.17,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "this"?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.29,0:40:26.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seems to have completely forgotten the "get out" thing
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.65,0:40:27.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Even more so than
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.04,0:40:31.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Prepare for the start of the show 3-2-1
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.66,0:40:37.39,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.39,0:40:42.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,To the point of being completely unintelligible
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.95,0:40:45.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, we revealed the truth at this point
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.52,0:40:51.13,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Didn't say "get out" at all
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.49,0:40:52.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,KOO
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.56,0:40:55.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did you forget to say "get out"?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.27,0:41:02.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.15,0:41:10.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In conclusion, the winner of the lecture contest is Nana Suzuki
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.26,0:41:14.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.61,0:41:17.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The Suzuki Nana part is too shocking
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.13,0:41:18.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A little too scary
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.22,0:41:20.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Quite impressive
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.13,0:41:22.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This kind of person being angry
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.09,0:41:24.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They really emit a different kind of terror
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.16,0:41:25.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's really shocking
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.90,0:41:33.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is that an act? I can't help but feel that she's actually like that
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.28,0:41:35.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Scary indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.48,0:41:40.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,To sum up, the lecture in the...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.54,0:41:44.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's pretty impressive. All kinds of things happened
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.12,0:41:50.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Very scary stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.00,0:41:56.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I also hope that Obon Kobon will continue to work hard
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.53,0:41:59.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.16,0:42:03.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I can't get out
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.21,0:42:10.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's all over for you. Just go. It's over
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.77,0:42:14.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I can't go
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.39,0:42:16.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So scary
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.65,0:42:22.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What a horrible exit
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.97,0:42:24.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's it. Thank you all
Dialogue: 2,0:42:27.57,0:42:33.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Now is everybody's theories
Dialogue: 2,0:42:34.38,0:42:36.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Tonight's presenter is
Dialogue: 2,0:42:38.12,0:42:41.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kenji Tamura
Dialogue: 2,0:42:44.82,0:42:50.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As stars, you must have all received letters from our fans, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:42:50.83,0:42:54.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Are there any letters that are particularly impressive?
Dialogue: 2,0:42:54.36,0:42:55.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What have you received Naomi?
Dialogue: 2,0:42:55.55,0:42:58.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A letter written about dating me
Dialogue: 2,0:42:58.67,0:42:59.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That we're in a relationship
Dialogue: 2,0:43:00.18,0:43:02.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although long-distant, he made a lot of effort
Dialogue: 2,0:43:03.39,0:43:04.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Very daring
Dialogue: 2,0:43:04.81,0:43:08.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He would call me and say he was sorry and all that
Dialogue: 2,0:43:10.02,0:43:11.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's delusional, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:43:11.23,0:43:14.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He was carrying out this series of activities by delusions of grandeur
Dialogue: 2,0:43:14.90,0:43:16.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And also say "I really want to see you"
Dialogue: 2,0:43:16.18,0:43:18.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"But we can't see each other because of Yoshimoto's rules."
Dialogue: 1,0:43:18.75,0:43:20.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So scary
Dialogue: 2,0:43:20.08,0:43:21.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It was like that
Dialogue: 2,0:43:21.86,0:43:23.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Have you received any strange things in the mail along with fan letters?
Dialogue: 2,0:43:23.92,0:43:26.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I once received a seemingly ordinary letter
Dialogue: 2,0:43:26.79,0:43:29.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It says "I'd like to be by your side to support you, but I can't."
Dialogue: 2,0:43:29.45,0:43:31.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"That's why I'm giving it this you as my stand-in"
Dialogue: 2,0:43:32.41,0:43:33.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then sent a clay doll over
Dialogue: 2,0:43:35.52,0:43:38.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The thing that guards the dead
Dialogue: 2,0:43:39.37,0:43:40.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That should be placed around the deceased
Dialogue: 2,0:43:41.95,0:43:43.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I thought I was still alive and well
Dialogue: 2,0:43:44.02,0:43:47.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, today I bring a theory about fan letters
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.61,0:43:48.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please take a look
Dialogue: 2,0:43:49.82,0:43:54.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Comedians receive memorable and creepy fan letters
Dialogue: 2,0:43:54.65,0:43:55.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 2,0:43:56.59,0:44:00.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We just talked about a lot of creepy things just now
Dialogue: 2,0:44:00.50,0:44:03.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do you have any experiences of this? Being in the idol industry
Dialogue: 2,0:44:04.15,0:44:06.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because the firm checks everything in advance
Dialogue: 2,0:44:06.37,0:44:07.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If it contains strange things...
Dialogue: 2,0:44:07.73,0:44:09.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It will be checked in advance. \N-Yes
Dialogue: 2,0:44:09.18,0:44:11.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For example, if an address is written on it, they'll cut it out
Dialogue: 2,0:44:11.69,0:44:14.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Or use markers to black it out, etc
Dialogue: 2,0:44:14.56,0:44:16.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So I haven't experienced this sort of thing
Dialogue: 2,0:44:17.10,0:44:21.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ok, so this time we asked people from all walks of life
Dialogue: 2,0:44:22.87,0:44:25.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And the only one with the least stringent inspection system was that of comedians
Dialogue: 2,0:44:27.66,0:44:28.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They just get random gifts
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.74,0:44:29.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They're delivered in the same way
Dialogue: 2,0:44:29.90,0:44:30.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They send anything to us
Dialogue: 2,0:44:30.94,0:44:33.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I also received a letter that was so thick that it was strange
Dialogue: 2,0:44:33.95,0:44:41.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Comedians receive memorable and creepy fan letters
Dialogue: 2,0:44:42.05,0:44:44.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Creepy fan letter ①
Dialogue: 2,0:44:44.65,0:44:46.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Cookie
Dialogue: 1,0:44:44.84,0:44:45.87,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,You're the creepiest, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:44:48.50,0:44:51.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What impressed me the most was
Dialogue: 2,0:44:51.67,0:44:54.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,About 3~4 years after debuting
Dialogue: 2,0:44:54.90,0:44:57.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There was a girl who was so short it was hilarious
Dialogue: 1,0:44:57.22,0:44:58.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So rude
Dialogue: 2,0:44:58.11,0:45:00.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She was a brunette with hair like a doll
Dialogue: 2,0:45:00.08,0:45:02.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The appearance was really like a Japanese doll
Dialogue: 2,0:45:02.56,0:45:03.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But with normal clothes on
Dialogue: 2,0:45:04.25,0:45:06.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The girl appeared suddenly
Dialogue: 2,0:45:06.32,0:45:08.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She often came to see my show
Dialogue: 2,0:45:08.82,0:45:11.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She had folded a thousand paper cranes
Dialogue: 2,0:45:11.25,0:45:14.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She handed me a thousand paper cranes with a red wabi-sabi design
Dialogue: 2,0:45:14.79,0:45:18.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then he said to me, "Please take it"
Dialogue: 2,0:45:18.26,0:45:19.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I then received a thousand paper cranes
Dialogue: 2,0:45:19.70,0:45:23.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When I got home, I unfolded them
Dialogue: 2,0:45:23.28,0:45:25.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Restored the paper to its original state
Dialogue: 2,0:45:25.60,0:45:28.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,On the reverse side of the pattern, in small letters, it read
Dialogue: 2,0:45:28.97,0:45:32.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"I hope you will like me", written all over it
Dialogue: 2,0:45:33.03,0:45:37.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A fan letter in the form of a thousand paper cranes
Dialogue: 2,0:45:38.41,0:45:42.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You know how some people can write characters on a grain of rice? It was like that
Dialogue: 2,0:45:42.45,0:45:44.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Must've used a super fine pen
Dialogue: 2,0:45:45.17,0:45:47.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Creepy fan letter ②
Dialogue: 2,0:45:48.03,0:45:49.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kamaitachi's Yamauchi
Dialogue: 2,0:45:51.83,0:45:54.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I received a postcard
Dialogue: 2,0:45:54.00,0:45:57.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was told that "I have a fan letter for you"
Dialogue: 2,0:45:57.07,0:46:00.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,On the front, it said "To Kenji Yamauchi"
Dialogue: 2,0:46:00.54,0:46:04.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then on the back, "I've been watching your show on TV"
Dialogue: 2,0:46:04.24,0:46:09.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"I support you from the bottom of my heart and look forward to hearing from you if I can."
Dialogue: 2,0:46:09.38,0:46:13.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"I'll be looking forward to hearing from you," it read
Dialogue: 2,0:46:13.28,0:46:15.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But the name on the front
Dialogue: 2,0:46:15.35,0:46:20.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Kenji Yamauchi" was written on a separate piece of paper
Dialogue: 2,0:46:20.76,0:46:22.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was curious about the extra bit of paper
Dialogue: 2,0:46:22.99,0:46:26.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So I carefully pulled it off
Dialogue: 2,0:46:26.06,0:46:29.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Underneath, it said "To Oguri Shun"
Dialogue: 2,0:46:29.17,0:46:32.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I thought, "Why'd you give up and compromise by sending it elsewhere?"
Dialogue: 2,0:46:32.57,0:46:34.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"This person is too determined to give up"
Dialogue: 2,0:46:34.90,0:46:39.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A letter from a determined fan
Dialogue: 2,0:46:39.98,0:46:43.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You'd think she'd at least rewrite it for me
Dialogue: 2,0:46:44.07,0:46:46.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Creepy fan letter ③
Dialogue: 2,0:46:46.94,0:46:48.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Viking's Kotouge
Dialogue: 1,0:46:48.70,0:46:49.49,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sent by a man?
Dialogue: 2,0:46:49.69,0:46:51.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well, it was sent by a male fan
Dialogue: 2,0:46:51.89,0:46:56.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He would wait for us at the exit after each performance
Dialogue: 2,0:46:57.23,0:47:00.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The fan letter was written on about 7 sheets of letterheaded paper
Dialogue: 2,0:47:00.50,0:47:04.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Kotouge's comedy is the source of my life and vitality"
Dialogue: 2,0:47:04.93,0:47:09.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The "Hearing your lines is like being caressed by lightning all over your body" kind of thing
Dialogue: 2,0:47:09.27,0:47:10.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Used language like a novel
Dialogue: 2,0:47:10.94,0:47:15.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then with another 3 sheets of paper
Dialogue: 2,0:47:15.28,0:47:17.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"I can't believe I just wrote 7 sheets."
Dialogue: 2,0:47:17.60,0:47:19.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He wrote an apology letter
Dialogue: 2,0:47:20.22,0:47:23.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Which was also included and sent in
Dialogue: 2,0:47:23.81,0:47:27.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He came to every show for about 4~5 years
Dialogue: 2,0:47:28.08,0:47:32.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,An emotional and apologetic fan letter
Dialogue: 2,0:47:32.92,0:47:35.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He works in an eel shop
Dialogue: 2,0:47:35.33,0:47:37.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 2,0:47:37.33,0:47:41.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At the end of the letter, he wrote the address and phone number of an eel shop
Dialogue: 2,0:47:41.76,0:47:46.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And his own cell phone number, email address and LINE ID
Dialogue: 2,0:47:46.21,0:47:48.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He was desperately trying to convey his personal information to me
Dialogue: 2,0:47:48.84,0:47:52.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then once, on a day off
Dialogue: 2,0:47:52.48,0:47:54.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd go to this eel store
Dialogue: 2,0:47:54.32,0:47:59.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It took about three and a half hours to drive there
Dialogue: 2,0:47:59.79,0:48:01.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It was already late afternoon when I reached it
Dialogue: 2,0:48:01.52,0:48:05.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I went in and found that this guy was not in because he had gone to dinner
Dialogue: 2,0:48:06.00,0:48:10.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then about a month later there was a show again
Dialogue: 2,0:48:10.73,0:48:13.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I got another letter
Dialogue: 2,0:48:13.97,0:48:18.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After reading it, I found there was a letter and something else
Dialogue: 2,0:48:18.07,0:48:20.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He put his work schedule in there
Dialogue: 2,0:48:20.21,0:48:23.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to work around your schedule!?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.51,0:48:28.05,note_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\pos(400,224)}Rest days other than the regular Monday holidays
Dialogue: 2,0:48:23.78,0:48:30.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Every time since then, the duty roster of that eel store has been put in the letter as a matter of course
Dialogue: 2,0:48:30.60,0:48:33.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Creepy fan letter ④
Dialogue: 2,0:48:33.66,0:48:34.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hiroshi
Dialogue: 2,0:48:35.69,0:48:37.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A house schematic
Dialogue: 2,0:48:37.49,0:48:40.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A layout of 2LDK was placed inside
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.49,0:48:41.40,note_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\pos(10,127)}{\blur4}※LDK indicates the layout of the house "L" stands for living room "D" stands for dining room "K" stands for kitchen 2LDK means two rooms and one bathroom
Dialogue: 2,0:48:40.00,0:48:41.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A letter was in there, too, and it said
Dialogue: 2,0:48:41.60,0:48:45.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"I rented this house to live in with Hiroshi"
Dialogue: 2,0:48:46.00,0:48:47.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"I've already arranged a guarantor"
Dialogue: 2,0:48:47.30,0:48:49.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Their signature and seal was on it too
Dialogue: 2,0:48:49.64,0:48:53.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then it said "All that's left is Hiroshi's signature and seal"
Dialogue: 2,0:48:53.68,0:48:55.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I haven't even met her
Dialogue: 2,0:48:56.11,0:49:00.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A fan letter describing having taken the liberty of finding a home for the both of them
Dialogue: 1,0:48:59.19,0:49:00.17,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is very similar to Naomi's
Dialogue: 2,0:49:00.88,0:49:06.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And it also said "Please pay the rent every month"
Dialogue: 2,0:49:07.08,0:49:09.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Creepy fan letter ⑤
Dialogue: 2,0:49:09.91,0:49:11.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Audrey's Kasuga
Dialogue: 2,0:49:12.73,0:49:14.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How can I put it? What I always see is
Dialogue: 2,0:49:14.80,0:49:21.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"I will visit you at a certain time on a certain day in a certain month, please wait for me at that time."
Dialogue: 1,0:49:19.10,0:49:20.20,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,His address was leaked
Dialogue: 2,0:49:21.30,0:49:25.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I also get these fan letters that want to control my schedule
Dialogue: 2,0:49:25.74,0:49:29.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I also received a lot of fan mail directly at my home
Dialogue: 2,0:49:29.28,0:49:31.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't you get scared when this happens?
Dialogue: 2,0:49:31.75,0:49:33.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Usually'd be scared
Dialogue: 2,0:49:34.18,0:49:36.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But they're kind enough to warn me in advance
Dialogue: 2,0:49:36.04,0:49:37.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 2,0:49:37.25,0:49:39.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But once there was no warning at all and I came home to find someone waiting for me
Dialogue: 2,0:49:40.92,0:49:44.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For Kasuga whose address was public
Dialogue: 1,0:49:43.53,0:49:44.82,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,How long have you been living here?
Dialogue: 2,0:49:44.56,0:49:48.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not only fan letters, but also gifts were also sent to his home
Dialogue: 2,0:49:49.73,0:49:52.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When I had a cold
Dialogue: 2,0:49:52.57,0:49:55.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I had a lot of things piled up in front of my house, condolences and so on
Dialogue: 2,0:49:55.80,0:49:58.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It made me feel like I was dying
Dialogue: 2,0:49:58.31,0:50:00.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I felt like "i'm not dead yet!"
Dialogue: 2,0:50:00.41,0:50:03.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Bouquet of flowers, drinks, and so on
Dialogue: 2,0:50:03.77,0:50:07.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In the middle of that was a refrigerated box
Dialogue: 2,0:50:07.02,0:50:08.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I thought "what is this?" and opened it
Dialogue: 2,0:50:08.25,0:50:11.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There was some porridge inside
Dialogue: 2,0:50:11.69,0:50:16.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A refrigerator full of porridge
Dialogue: 1,0:50:13.35,0:50:14.34,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's awful
Dialogue: 2,0:50:16.84,0:50:17.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 2,0:50:18.26,0:50:21.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Another thing was placed in front of my house
Dialogue: 2,0:50:21.83,0:50:26.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Like a garbage bag, something big
Dialogue: 2,0:50:26.17,0:50:29.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I thought "it's another prank or something"
Dialogue: 2,0:50:30.41,0:50:34.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I grabbed the garbage bag and tried to remove it
Dialogue: 2,0:50:34.48,0:50:39.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then a hand suddenly grabbed me from below
Dialogue: 2,0:50:39.72,0:50:41.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Inside the garbage bag...
Dialogue: 2,0:50:41.15,0:50:42.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There was a woman
Dialogue: 2,0:50:42.84,0:50:44.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A woman?
Dialogue: 2,0:50:44.99,0:50:49.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A surprise appearance from a garbage bag
Dialogue: 2,0:50:50.03,0:50:53.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I tried not to react too strongly
Dialogue: 2,0:50:54.03,0:50:56.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I said "can you get out of the way?"
Dialogue: 2,0:50:56.20,0:51:00.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The person said "ok, ok fine" etc
Dialogue: 2,0:51:00.04,0:51:02.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She probably thought i'd be a little more exaggerated
Dialogue: 2,0:51:03.48,0:51:05.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Creepy fan letter ⑥
Dialogue: 2,0:51:06.57,0:51:08.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nonstyle's Inoue
Dialogue: 2,0:51:09.48,0:51:13.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There was a letter full of how much the person liked me
Dialogue: 1,0:51:12.34,0:51:13.04,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This dumb guy
Dialogue: 2,0:51:13.35,0:51:19.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then she said, "The students in my class don't know what's good about Inoue."
Dialogue: 2,0:51:19.59,0:51:24.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"That's why I'm always talking about Inoue during break time or after school."
Dialogue: 2,0:51:24.93,0:51:31.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"I desperately explained to the entire class, including the teacher" something like that
Dialogue: 2,0:51:31.30,0:51:33.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then I suddenly saw the next page which read
Dialogue: 2,0:51:33.47,0:51:38.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"After doing so, I was gradually bullied by everyone."
Dialogue: 2,0:51:38.74,0:51:43.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Fan letter expressing bullying
Dialogue: 1,0:51:40.04,0:51:40.76,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Poor thing
Dialogue: 2,0:51:44.01,0:51:46.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Creepy fan letter (7)
Dialogue: 2,0:51:47.14,0:51:50.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Higashibukuro
Dialogue: 2,0:51:51.59,0:51:55.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I had a scandal in the second half of 2013
Dialogue: 2,0:51:55.56,0:51:57.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Fans were almost reduced to 0
Dialogue: 2,0:51:57.99,0:52:00.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Basically just one person waiting for me at the exit during that time
Dialogue: 2,0:52:01.03,0:52:02.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She gave me a letter
Dialogue: 2,0:52:02.90,0:52:03.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But after reading it
Dialogue: 2,0:52:03.97,0:52:07.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Even with a scandal like that, I have a way to redeem you."
Dialogue: 2,0:52:07.26,0:52:08.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wrote something like
Dialogue: 2,0:52:10.17,0:52:15.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Ask someone for guidance, and your past will be cleansed."
Dialogue: 2,0:52:15.54,0:52:19.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"The only way to purify all this is to enter this religion."
Dialogue: 2,0:52:19.31,0:52:22.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And then they were persistently trying to persuade me to join the church
Dialogue: 2,0:52:22.55,0:52:25.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What did she look like?
Dialogue: 2,0:52:25.92,0:52:29.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really short and with a doll's haircut
Dialogue: 2,0:52:29.88,0:52:34.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Fan letter to strongly persuade others using mind tricks
Dialogue: 1,0:52:31.40,0:52:33.60,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is it the same person as the previous one?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.72,0:52:35.07,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This picture is reused
Dialogue: 2,0:52:35.23,0:52:37.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Creepy fan letter ⑧
Dialogue: 1,0:52:35.85,0:52:36.55,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 2,0:52:38.17,0:52:39.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ungirls' Tanaka
Dialogue: 1,0:52:38.17,0:52:39.00,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,No way
Dialogue: 2,0:52:40.54,0:52:45.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I said something like I have 100 million in savings on a TV show
Dialogue: 2,0:52:45.97,0:52:49.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Got fan letters like "Can you lend me 2 million"
Dialogue: 2,0:52:49.55,0:52:53.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Fan letter with Tanaka's cash in mind
Dialogue: 2,0:52:54.28,0:52:56.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What were they going to do with the 2 million?
Dialogue: 2,0:52:56.85,0:52:58.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It seems like a lot has happened
Dialogue: 2,0:52:58.55,0:53:03.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"I have 2 million in debts"
Dialogue: 2,0:53:04.03,0:53:08.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"I cant live and pay the interest"
Dialogue: 2,0:53:09.06,0:53:12.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So I need to pay back 2 million first
Dialogue: 2,0:53:12.87,0:53:15.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I want to pay all the debts together
Dialogue: 2,0:53:15.64,0:53:18.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ten it said, "I will belong to Tanaka"
Dialogue: 2,0:53:18.47,0:53:20.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Three letters have been sent from the same person
Dialogue: 2,0:53:20.91,0:53:24.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The third letter had the repayment plan written on it
Dialogue: 2,0:53:24.88,0:53:27.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,40,000 per month
Dialogue: 2,0:53:27.82,0:53:30.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It'd take a little over 5 years to pay back the money
Dialogue: 2,0:53:30.32,0:53:32.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If they paid back 40,000 a month
Dialogue: 2,0:53:32.20,0:53:34.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They also wanted an extra 10,000 for themselves
Dialogue: 2,0:53:34.12,0:53:37.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Said it should be possible with your salary
Dialogue: 2,0:53:37.26,0:53:40.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Said they wanted to go to various places to play
Dialogue: 2,0:53:40.26,0:53:42.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Want to learn English conversation
Dialogue: 2,0:53:42.76,0:53:46.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You should forget English conversation for the moment
Dialogue: 2,0:53:46.00,0:53:49.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't the extra 10,000 be returned to me as well?
Dialogue: 2,0:53:49.84,0:53:51.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Should pay me back 50,000 a month
Dialogue: 2,0:53:52.07,0:53:55.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Surely too naive
Dialogue: 2,0:53:56.19,0:53:57.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Finally
Dialogue: 2,0:54:01.84,0:54:04.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Creepy fan letter ⑨
Dialogue: 2,0:54:04.94,0:54:06.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Egashira 2:50
Dialogue: 2,0:54:07.92,0:54:12.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,20 years ago in the first month I checked the mailbox in front of my house
Dialogue: 2,0:54:12.43,0:54:14.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Inside was a New Year's card
Dialogue: 2,0:54:14.80,0:54:16.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then I looked at the reverse side
Dialogue: 2,0:54:16.30,0:54:18.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It read "Happy New Year"
Dialogue: 2,0:54:19.00,0:54:20.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It was written in pubic hair!
Dialogue: 2,0:54:21.18,0:54:25.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,New Year's greeting card with a pubic hair
Dialogue: 2,0:54:26.04,0:54:30.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If it was a woman it'd be okay but it was a man so I feel super disgusted
Dialogue: 2,0:54:30.46,0:54:33.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0201FB&\3c&HFFFFFF&}In summary\N{\3c\c}That's about the extent of what can be said on TV
Dialogue: 2,0:54:33.92,0:54:34.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 2,0:54:35.34,0:54:36.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you mean it's okay if it was a woman?
Dialogue: 2,0:54:36.67,0:54:37.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 2,0:54:39.00,0:54:40.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But there are really ones that want to borrow money
Dialogue: 2,0:54:40.77,0:54:43.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The private messages on the social media have a bunch of these
Dialogue: 2,0:54:44.05,0:54:45.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Want to borrow money from you?
Dialogue: 2,0:54:45.15,0:54:45.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Loads!
Dialogue: 2,0:54:47.17,0:54:48.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You also get them?
Dialogue: 2,0:54:48.18,0:54:48.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 2,0:54:48.81,0:54:50.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not really anymore
Dialogue: 2,0:54:50.22,0:54:51.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But there used to be from time to time
Dialogue: 2,0:54:51.90,0:54:54.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I did lend some
Dialogue: 2,0:54:54.79,0:54:55.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's a lie, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:54:57.95,0:54:59.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't start!
Dialogue: 2,0:54:59.57,0:55:01.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because of the silence so you must be lying
Dialogue: 2,0:55:01.92,0:55:02.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So obvious
